INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (69,1,'2023-01-15 14:11:18','2023-01-15 14:11:18','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\">Learn Java</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Learn Java course is a comprehensive introduction to the Java programming language. It is designed for beginners who have little or no programming experience, but it is also suitable for experienced programmers who want to learn Java. The course covers all the essential concepts of the Java language and its standard libraries, from the basics of variables and data types to more advanced topics such as object-oriented programming, exception handling, and file input/output.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The course is divided into multiple videos, each covering a specific topic. The videos are well-structured, and easy to follow, and include examples, exercises, and quizzes to help you understand the concepts better. The course covers the following topics:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/shantanukhond/LearnJava#appendix-for-learn-java-youtube-video-series\"></a>Appendix for \"Learn Java\" YouTube video series:</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><a href=\"https://github.com/shantanukhond/LearnJava#learn-java-2-variables-and-literals-in-java\"></a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aX0DE1hVWMo&amp;t\">Learn Java: 2 Variables and Literals in Java</a></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>This video provides an introduction to variables and literals in Java. It covers how to declare and initialize variables of different data types, including primitives and non-primitives, and how to use literals to assign values to them.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Additionally, the video also covers the scope of variables and how it is affected by different code blocks,