rning more advanced topics like concurrency and web development. This course is a great starting point for anyone who wants to become a Java developer or simply wants to learn to code.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Link to Series: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLH1gsHiD7JxhtWH9_HzGU1kZ6hPzn6ICD\" target=\"_blank\">Learn Java</a><br>Link to GitHub: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/shantanukhond/LearnJava\" target=\"_blank\">shantanukhond/LearnJava</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Learn Java','','inherit','closed','closed','','63-revision-v1','','','2023-01-15 14:11:18','2023-01-15 14:11:18','',63,'http://shantanukhond.local/?p=69',0,'revision','',0);
